<section class="section02 giada11 giada12">
    <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="section-title">
                <h2>Mobile application for online booking</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12 section-description">
                <p>Mobile application helps the business to be open 24 hours a day. It’s the optimal solution, if you aim to increase the number of repeat sales. According to our statistics, over 50% of users make appointments in beauty salons, ateliers, clinics with mobile devices. Application for clients booking is the direct work with clients, it’s an important image component of a company, that cares about clients and about increasing the sales in the long term.</p>
                <h4>Thanks to mobile application you get</h4>
                <ul class="Glist">
                    <li>consumers’ loyalty</li>
                    <li>repeat purchases</li>
                    <li>widening of client base with regular visitors’ recommends</li>
                </ul>
                <p>The key advantage of YCLIENTS mobile application – is almost instant solution of the client’s problem. The customer takes minimum actions, quickly gets the result, and he doesn’t spend money on phone talks. The application becomes an analog of loyalty card: it’s enough to us it in order to participate in the loyalty program.</p>

                <p>The personal mobile application for online booking contains the individual set of options and it integrates with automated system of business management. It’s easy to install it, adjust and use it.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

